    "Having students enter the vignettes rather than health professionals ensured that only information stated in the vignettes were entered without subjective clinical interpretation of symptoms, which could introduce bias 17.",
    "The two students entered each vignette into 12 different SAAs (amounting to 540 assessments).",
    "The selection of SAAs was based on our comparator dataset 13 to ensure comparability.",
    "The original study from which this dataset is derived had systematically identified all publicly available SAAs.",
    "For our study, we had to exclude certain SAAs because four were no longer available, two discontinued providing triage advice, two had shifted to a subscription model, and two now give specialized advice for pediatric cases."
  ],
